This is a ruble for Aptana Studio 3. This ruble enables Drupal 7 Hooks inside of the command menu.

INSTALL

To install this ruble, copy the drupal.ruble folder and all it's contents to the
$USER_DOCUMENT_DIRECTORY/Aptana Rubles/ directory. The $USER_DOCUMENT_DIRECTORY is platform independent.
On Windows 7 you will find this directory under c:\users\{username}\Aptana Rubles\

**NOTE: This project is in the very early phases of development. Any help on future features and enhancements is greatly appreciated. 